  "description": "A recolor of Iron Ore to look more like its counterparts.",
  "body": "A more accurate look to one of the first ores in the game!\n\nA very small resource pack that recolors the iron ore.\n\nIncludes support for the [Universal Ores](https://modrinth.com/mod/universal_ores) mod!\n\n![Iron Ore and Deepslate Iron Ore](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c3fb523d05383a85221c80b81101874c1b54f734.png)\n\nIf you would like connected and emissive textures, go here: [Accurate Iron Ore CTM](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/accurate-iron-ore-ctm) \n\nTo install, just open your .minecraft/resourcepacks and throw the zip file in for your version. Then go into Minecraft, Options, Resource Packs, and add it, and you are good to go!\n\nI hope you enjoy it!",
